    "description": {
      "zh": "草原枪械工坊（Prarie Gun Works）消音器专为C14中程狙击武器系统（MRSWS）设计，采用与MK12 SPR所用AEM5消音器相同的套筒式结构，具备极低的枪声特征。该消音器在抑制噪音的同时，几乎不会造成弹着点偏移，至今仍是加拿大军队的精选产品。",
      "en": "The Prarie Gun Works sound suppressor designed to be used as a part of the C14 Medium Range Sniper Weapon System (MRSWS) boasts a very quiet report, using the same style sleeving suppressor as the AEM5 suppressor used by the MK12 SPR. While keeping the noise down, it also has a very limited POI shift, making it perfect for the Canadian army that uses it to this day."
    },
